{"tid":261921,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"男子持槍自轟，死唔去子彈穿頭後射殺女友","createTime":"2017-05-28T23:20:44.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-30T03:58:55.000Z","uid":41351,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"cee3d8e85171df10eecda7ae8a1c2eff7febb5ec","tid":261921,"uid":41351,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-28T23:20:44.000Z","msg":"美國阿拉斯加州一名男子疑開槍向頭部自轟，豈料子彈穿過他頭骨，打中22歲女友胸口，女友最後重傷不治，男子卻活了下來，他現被控二級謀殺罪。<br />\n<br />\n案發在上月19日凌晨，檢察官指21歲的西布森（Victor Sibson）向自己頭部開槍時，與他拍拖多年的女朋友、22歲的哈格（Brittanymae Haag）企圖阻止，豈料子彈穿過西布森的頭部後打中哈格。救護員發現哈格時，她躺在地上胸口大量出血，兩人隨即被送院搶救，西布森頭部受傷、撿回一命，哈格卻傷重死亡。<br />\n西布森曾向探員透露，不記得自己曾經開槍。戴著保護頭盔的他上周二出庭，否認控罪。他在庭上向法官表示自己失業，沒錢聘請代表律師，「我們能否今天就決定我是否有罪？」<br />\n由於他未能交出25萬美元（195萬港元）保釋金，目前被還柙，等候8月21日再應訊，一旦他被定罪，最高刑罰為監禁99年。<br />\n美國廣播公司/英國《都市報》  <br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/international/20170529/56753008\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Finternational%2F20170529%2F56753008&d=6EYkUlC4fZClXY%2B%2FZB2rRcPrXSGIZiPsBFv3mRhlVuk%3D&h=f37efb6c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Finternational%2F20170529%2F56753008&h=aae016bc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/international/20170529/56753008</a><br />\n離奇係咁樣都可以判謀殺"},{"pid":"11c4e5f992d0d4d197be1bc86b852815c18aad42","tid":261921,"uid":33481,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-30T03:34:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bbab70c27b3db92e59419abe12c322bcebe4e92c","tid":261921,"uid":59886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-30T03:53:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c8e3633b28e34244a9c9cf1623c38fac2daa9385","tid":261921,"uid":8171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-30T03:58:55.000Z","msg":"讓子彈飛 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}